variables.name: Message
variables.value: You time traveled back in time with that time machine you found. Your goal is to obtain the three ancient artifacts: the mummy, the jade dragon, and the helmet of Julius Caesar. You are armed with a magic coin that shoots coins. You appear to be in ancient Egypt. Go get the mummy, but beware. A skeleton guards it. Level 1 begins...
